727999f-b.title: Queens: South Road - 55th Street
727999f-b.text:
South Road, south side, at, adioining and east of 155th Street, showing in a set of two views the Amos Denton house, raised and remodeled. This was known as the Ab. De Bevoise house, from 1860-1891, oN which Gasper Phraner was the owner at a later date.
1922.
View 2: May 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
